@node ALURE "Aluren"

@{b}Aluren@{ub}

Color   = Green
Rarity  = TP(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 2GG
Artist  = April Lee

Text(TP): Any player may play a creature card with total casting cost 3 or
          less whenever he or she could play an instant and without
          paying its casting cost.

Flavor Text: @{i}Squee bounced up and down. "I see a horsey, an' a piggy, an'
               a --" "If you don't shut up," hissed Mirri, "you'll see a
               kidney and a spleeny."

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_A.guide/ALURE

@endnode
