@{b}Apes of Rath@{ub}

Color   = Green
Rarity  = TP(U)
Type    = Summon Apes(5/4)
Cost    = 2GG
Artist  = Jeff Laubenstein

Text(TP): If Apes of Rath attacks, it does not untap during your next
          untap phase.

Flavor Text: @{i}Monkeys three, monkeys through.

 @{b}No Rulings@{ub}
@endnode
